OL,3,CDefence closes case in Sir Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson sex offences trial
OL,6,FThe defence in Sir Jeffrey Donaldson's
OL,7,Ftrial over historical sex offences has
OL,8,Fclosed its case.
OL,10,FThe former DUP leader's barrister told
OL,11,FNewry Crown Court on Monday afternoon
OL,12,Fthat no further evidence would be
OL,13,Fcalled.
OL,15,FThe 63-year-old has pleaded not guilty
OL,16,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
