OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781552859
OL,3,CDefence closes case in Sir Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson sex offences trial
OL,6,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,7,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,8,Fand gross indecency, and span a period
OL,9,Fbetween 1985 and 2008 involving two
OL,10,Falleged victims.
OL,12,FComplainant A and B have both given
OL,13,Fevidence at the trial.
OL,15,FBoth women allege they were abused as
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,FLady Eleanor Donaldson, 60 denies
OL,19,Fseveral charges of aiding and abetting
OL,20,Fher husband's alleged offending.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
