PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781552859
OL,3,CDefence closes case in Sir Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson sex offences trial
OL,6,FShe is facing a trial of the facts on
OL,7,Fmental health grounds.
OL,9,FThe trial of the facts will test the
OL,10,Fevidence in the case, but cannot
OL,11,Fresult in a criminal conviction.
OL,13,FJeffrey Donaldson spent two days in
OL,14,Fthe witness box giving evidence in the
OL,15,Ftrial last week.
OL,17,FHis barrister Kieran Vaughan KC told
OL,18,Fthe jury of seven men and five women
OL,19,Fon Monday that he was "now in a
OL,20,Fposition to close my case".
