OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781552859
OL,3,CDefence closes case in Sir Jeffrey
OL,4,CDonaldson sex offences trial
OL,6,FBarrister for Eleanor Donaldson, Ian
OL,7,FTurkington KC, said: "She is incapable
OL,8,Fof giving evidence so we don't intend
OL,9,Fto call any further evidence."
OL,11,FClosing submissions are expected to
OL,12,Fbegin on Tuesday morning.
